<br>
If you want to go with the &quot;typical&quot; role for a warrior on a raid, the typical role for a warrior on a raid is as a damage dealer.  Obviously, it depends on the size of your raids and the targets, but we typically send in one or two warriors on a mob to tank it and the other 5-10 warriors at the raid try to stay low enough on the agro list to avoid stealing the agro.   <p><I>"Increase my killing power, eh?"<BR> 
